<%- include('partials/header') %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
<title>Home | Ultimax Logistics LTD</title>
<body class="home-page">
    <h2 class="welcome-text">Welcome To Ultimax Logistics Limited</h2>
    <section class="aboutUs" id="aboutUs">
        <h2 class="aboutUs-text">
            Ultimax Logistics Limited (ULL) is an indigenous firm set up in 2012. 
            It was incorporated under the companies and allied matters decree of Nigeria, 1968. 
            Ultimax Logistics Limited was established with the aim of providing a wide range of services such as:
        </h2>
        <div class="services" id="services">
            <% services.forEach(service => { %>
                <div class="services-card">
                    <img src="/images/<%= service.img %>" alt="<%= service.title %>" class="service-image">
                    <h3 class="service-title"><%= service.title %></h3>
                    <p class="service-description"></p> 
                </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
        <div class="proposal-scope" id="scope">
            <h3 class="proposal-heading">CLIENTâ€™S REQUIREMENTS / PROPOSAL SCOPE</h3>
            <p>
                ULL is pleased to make/forward this proposal, highlighting our capability with respect to the services listed above.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>ULL</strong> has extensive expertise in the area of travel and meet/greet services in various airports in the country.
                We are able to assist Client in the provision of the required services. 
                We would assist various companies navigate the bureaucratic and time-consuming process of commuting to various designation in Nigeria.
            </p>
            <p>
                Specifically, this proposal is limited to the provision of the following services for the benefit of Client:
            </p>
            <ol>
                <li>Provision of meet and greet services</li>
                <li>Provision of ticketing and reservation services</li>
                <li>Other travel related services that might be requested by Client</li>
            </ol>
            <p>
                We welcome any opportunity to expand the scope of the services contained in this proposal and where such additional services are required,
                we would agree the terms and conditions prior to the commencement of such services.
            </p>
            <p>Some of our clients include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Poseidon Energy Services Limited</li>
                <li>Desicon Engineering Limited</li>
                <li>Kerex Nigeria Limited</li>
                <li>Boskel Nigeria Limited</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="contactUs" id="contactUs">
        <h2 class="contactUs-heading">Contact Us</h2>
        <form id="contactForm" class="contact-form">
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
            <button id="contact-button">Send Message</button>
            <p id="formMessage" class="formMessage"></p>
        </form>
    </section>
</body>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<script src="/js/index.js" defer></script>
